Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.02,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I wonder if following the theory of love is the right thing to do...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.82,0:00:22.50,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I undo my ponytail and sigh in the mirror
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.50,0:00:29.50,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I wonder how I look in your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.00,0:00:36.76,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I can feel exciting things coming, just like in those girly comics
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.76,0:00:43.14,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I put on my usual facade, wondering if you can see through me
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.69,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}Even though you were closer than anyone else
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.69,0:00:50.23,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}Even though we were getting along better than anyone else
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.23,0:00:57.16,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}For some reason, until yesterday the distance between us was somewhat painful
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.41,0:01:05.16,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}According to the theory of love, a girl grows up every time her heart skips a beat
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.16,0:01:11.55,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}I'm not a child anymore, and yet I don't know how to react when you praise me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.55,0:01:19.30,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,140)\be4}"Don't make me worry", you say, as you take my hand and never let it go
